TITLE: Creating Line Series Chart in TradingView Lightweight Charts
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create and configure a line series chart with time-series data. The example shows initialization of chart options, creating a line series, setting data points, and fitting content to the time scale.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tradingview/lightweight-charts/blob/master/website/docs/series-types.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_5

