TITLE: Creating Volume Histogram Overlay Series in TradingView
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add a volume histogram series as an overlay to the main chart. Sets up the volume series with appropriate price formatting and positioning using scale margins.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tradingview/lightweight-charts/blob/master/website/tutorials/how_to/price-and-volume.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const volumeSeries = chart.addSeries(HistogramSeries, {
    priceFormat: {
        type: 'volume',
    },
    priceScaleId: '', // set as an overlay by setting a blank priceScaleId
});
volumesSeries.priceScale().applyOptions({
    // set the positioning of the volume series
    scaleMargins: {
        top: 0.7, // highest point of the series will be 70% away from the top
        bottom: 0,
    },
});
