TITLE: Converting Times Using date-fns-tz Library
DESCRIPTION: A JavaScript function that uses the date-fns-tz library to convert UTC timestamps to a specified time zone. This approach is slightly faster than the pure Date API solution but requires an additional dependency.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tradingview/lightweight-charts/blob/master/website/docs/time-zones.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { utcToZonedTime } from 'date-fns-tz';

function timeToTz(originalTime, timeZone) {
    const zonedDate = utcToZonedTime(new Date(originalTime * 1000), timeZone);
    return zonedDate.getTime() / 1000;
}
```

