TITLE: Defining ExamplesList Component in JSX
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines an ExamplesList component that retrieves and renders a list of 'Examples / Demos' links from the documentation sidebar.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tradingview/lightweight-charts/blob/master/website/tutorials/index.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
export const ExamplesList = () => {
	const examplesCategory = useDocsSidebar().items.find(
		item => item.type === "category" && item.label === "Examples / Demos"
	);
	const examples = examplesCategory.items.filter(doc => doc.type === "link");
	return (
		<ul>
			{examples.map(docLink => (
				<li key={docLink.docId}>
					<a href={docLink.href}>{docLink.label}</a>
				</li>
			))}
		</ul>
	);
};
```

